*Attention Package owner,This is to inform you that a delivery company
contacted my law firmregarding your unclaimed package in their custody
which they intent tohand over to the government as unclaimed package,So am
contacting you to know if you are still interested in claimingthe package
as it has  been with the Turkish customs for over a yearnow and they have
just  informed us that they will release it once youmeet the needed
delivery conditions.so contact me as soon as possible with this
email:(bharlesokoye@gmail.com <bharlesokoye@gmail.com>)  so that i will
direct you on what to doRegardsBar Charles*
